## Rate Limiting

```ruby
# Use Rack::Attack gem
gem 'rack-attack'

# config/initializers/rack_attack.rb
class Rack::Attack
  throttle('req/ip', limit: 300, period: 5.minutes) do |req|
    req.ip
  end
  
  throttle('logins/email', limit: 5, period: 20.seconds) do |req|
    req.params['email'] if req.path == '/login' && req.post?
  end
end
```

